channel.title: 10 track EP “Planets EP” out now!
channel.description:
After a few months of hard work I finally finished this 10 track EP.
It’s comprised of a Prelude, interlude and every planet in our solar system.
Here it is: https://soundcloud.com/colin-m-348193009/sets/planets-ep
My personal favourites are:
1: The Space Between (Interlude)
2:Neptune
3:Earth
Hope you enjoy!!!
